def all_paths
      results = []
      paths = routes.map(&:path)
      paths.each do |p|
        sub_paths = []
        parts = p.split('/')
        until parts.empty?
          parts.pop
          sub_path = parts.join('/')
          sub_paths << sub_path unless sub_path == ''
        end
        results += sub_paths
      end
      @all_paths = (results + paths).sort.uniq
    end
